  <scopecontent id="aspace_020d9896916eb789cd87f706e78c68f0">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Magazines, brochures, reports, manuscripts of stories, files, bulk mailings and miscellany relating to human sexuality in general and to homosexuality in particular. Subject files derive from sexuality and privacy commissions on which McWhirter served. Collection includes numerous typescripts of pornographic stories. Many of the items were in the Mariposa Research and Education Foundation library.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <relatedmaterial id="aspace_99dfc00d72bd3589b39a23fb625a9186">
    <head>RELATED MATERIAL</head>
<p>Bruce R. Voeller papers, #7307.</p><p> Several cubic feet of periodicals have been catalogued individually; clippings and straight magazines and newspapers were discarded.</p>  </relatedmaterial>
