  <acqinfo id="aspace_cb34bf0f491944753ca6aec714744fa3">
    <head>PROVENANCE</head>
<p>Many of the items were in the Mariposa Research and Education Foundation library. The provenance of the pornographic manuscripts is not clear. The Bruce Voeller manuscript <title>Murder at McGurk</title> was transferred to the Voeller Collection, #7307.</p>  </acqinfo>
